{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangetheme"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"metadata":{"title":"OrangeTheme","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeTheme"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B5ThemeC"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships"},{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/SQ","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme is the bsic, default, theme for any Orange products."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is an override of the abtract "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"must be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can override any properties from its superclass, and can be derived too."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Group","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"],"anchor":"Group"}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme\/init(borders:colors:colorModes:colorsCharts:colorsDecorative:effects:elevations:fonts:grids:opacities:dimensions:sizes:spaces:alert:badge:bar:bulletList:button:checkbox:chip:controlItem:divider:icon:link:pinCodeInput:quantityInput:radioButton:selectInput:skeleton:switch:tag:inputTag:textArea:textInput:resourcesBundle:name:fontFamily:tuning:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Usages","level":1,"anchor":"Usages"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Any Orange products must use this theme. It provides core and Orange colors and any elements for sizings, spacings and dimensions for example.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The system font families are used; no ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helevetica"}]},{"text":" font family is embeded nor providd  by OUDS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This theme also provides colors charts tokens.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be got through environment variable:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Integration","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Integration"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" and get it through environment variable."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Theme-tuning","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Theme tuning"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to "},{"code":"Tuning","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To apply the tuning:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Typography","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Typography"},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Helvetica Neue"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"code":"OrangeTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" uses as font family the token ","type":"text"},{"code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", which is today ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue\") \/\/ Which is font family nale"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Because the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"text"}]},{"text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"register them and define the font family name to use.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Tokens loading","anchor":"Tokens-loading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also use some tokens providers defined in your side, but they must match the same type as the one used on the themes (see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["   \/\/ Use some already defined providers","   let borders = OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider()","   let sizes = OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider()","   let spaces = OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ For example, use your own provider of color semantic tokens","   \/\/ It must inherit from OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider (which is instance of AllColorSemanticTokensProvider) or directly implement AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","   let colors = YourOwnColorSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Some providers need other providers to use their tokens","   let button = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(sizes: sizes, borders: borders, colors: colors, spaces: spaces)","","   \/\/ But you can also use the providers as they are without assigning semantic tokens providers","   \/\/ and just use the default ones","   let badge = OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Define in the end your theme by overriding some providers.","   \/\/ You can override all providers, or only some, or just keep the theme as is.","   \/\/ However you should uses thhese providers in a dedicated Orange theme subclass for clarity reasons.","   let yourOwnOrangeTheme = OrangeTheme(colors: colors, borders: borders, sizes: sizes, spaces: spaces, button: button, badge: badge)"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Tokens versions","anchor":"Tokens-versions"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Core OUDS version: 1.10.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Core Orange version: 1.2.0","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Brand Orange version: 2.5.0"}]}]}]},{"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.8.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s16SendableMetatypeP"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable"},"https://brand.orange.com/en/brand-basics/typography":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)"}],"title":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","type":"link","url":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTheme"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","title":"OUDSTheme","abstract":[{"text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A Swift ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"class"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to implement all tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme contract"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" is not a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"final","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" class, its type cannot be seen as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sendable"},{"text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"c